attr.title: OpenClaw
attr.desc: A Reimplementation of the 1997 Captain Claw platformer.
attr.desc_md: A Reimplementation of the 1997 Captain Claw platformer. Join forces with Captain Claw, the greatest cat pirate ever to challenge the Cocker Spaniard Armada! Embark on an epic quest to recover the lost gems of the Amulet of Nine Lives.
